Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Building 1, Equinox Business Park is located in the heart of Deakin which offers a mix of commercial and medical suites to occupiers.  Within proximity to the Parliamentary Triangle, Woden Town Centre and Canberra CBD, this is a prime location for a range of businesses.

The landmark Business Parks consists of three primary A grade buildings which allow a wide permitted use including office and medical.  Each has excellent natural light, efficient floor plates, lift access and services to meet an A grade standard.  Basement parking and on-site parking is available for occupiers and staff within the Business Park.  End of trip facilities are available for Staff as well as on site café EQ, Bakehouse and The Den Canberra.

Available for lease in Building 1:

Part Ground Floor: 235sqm* Open plan ready for fitout suitable for medical

Part level 2: 282sqm* Refurbished open plan space ready for fit out – good frontage onto central glass corridor. May be subdivided to two suites of 125sqm and 155sqm.

Level 3: 812sqm* Refurbished open plan space ready for fit out which includes a 122sqm* terrace


For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE.

*Approx.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: SUITABLE FOR A RANGE OF OFFICE USERS

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located in West Deakin this very functional building is offering multiple suites suitable for office and medical operators. The building features a central stair case as well as lift access to the upper floor and under croft parking. The building has recently undergone refurbishment works including bathroom and foyer enhancements. 

Only a short drive to Phillip, Barton and the CIty CBD this location offers amenity at your doorstep whilst being central in Canberra. Public transport is readily available and parking is within close proximity to the building.

Available for lease:

Ground Suite 4 - 200sqm* Cold shell ready for fit out, 5 parking spaces available.

Level 1 Suite 8 - 220sqm* Existing fit out in place which can be re-utilized or removed, 3 parking spaces available.

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE Canberra.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: HIGH QUALITY OFFICE & MEDICAL SPACE AVAILABLE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
2 King Street provides a rare and unique chance to secure your new commercial office space in the heart of Deakin with easy access to Woden, Canberra City and the Parliamentary Triangle. The building will also have direct access to stage two of the light rail with a stop proposed only a short distance away.  The building has been refurbished to the highest standard and offering a boutique and industrial style of office accommodation. 

Available for lease:

Unit 32 - 150sqm*:  Modern fit out in place which includes reception area, 6 offices, utilities/server room, meeting room and an internal kitchenette.

Building features include:
* High caliber tenancy mix including office & medical 
* Innovative design
* Onsite cafe
* Breakout areas for staff
* Designed to achieve 4.5 NABERS rating
* Abundance of natural light
* Independent air conditioning to each unit

Surrounding amenities include:
* Pool facility for lap swimming and hydro therapy
* Recreation ovals
* Cafes offering catering services
* Child care centre
* Medical and dental services
* Ample public parking available directly opposite the building

Please contact CBRE leasing agents for further information or to arrange an inspection.

*approx.

The medical precinct of Deakin is the address for many national associations and corporate entities. Its proximity to the Parliamentary triangle, CBD and Woden Town Centre allows convenient access to these important business hubs. 

Available for lease/sale is 168sqm* of office space across undivided ground floor units 3 & 4. The unit has an open plan fitout featuring an office, meeting room, reception and kitchenette. The tenancy boasts an abundance of parking with 8 allocated spaces at the rear of the building as well as ample public parking on Napier Close.

For further information or to arrange for an inspection please contact CBRE Canberra.

Approx*

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: OFFICE SPACE IN THE HEART OF DEAKIN'S MEDICAL PRECINCT

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Deakin.One is a new kind of workplace: One that nurtures its inhabitants and fosters – through its balance of design and amenity – a higher level of productivity and satisfaction.

Centrally located, Deakin.One is connected, close to major arterial routes linking it with the Canberra City CBD, Parliamentary Triangle and Canberra Airport.

With its outlook over serene green spaces and its high level of amenity, Deakin.One is the prefect location to combine work and wellness to promote collaborative thinking and to attract and retain the best talent in your industry.

This exciting new development features 8,000sqm of state of the art office accommodation over 3 levels connected by a central atrium allowing natural light to diffuse through the space. 

Key Highlights:

•	2 Levels of secure basement parking
•	Designed to achieve a 4.5- Star NABERS Rating
•	Market leading EOT facilities
•	Efficient floor plates
•	Proposed onsite café
•	Surrounded by amenity and green spaces
•	Suitable for office or medical

For further information please visit the website www.deakinone.com.au or contact the exclusive marketing agents.
